brogan.description:
A friendly hero in range gains 1 coin;
if any hero was defeated this round,
that friendly hero gains 3 coins instead.

A friendly hero in range gains 2 coin2;
if any hero was defeated this round,
that friendly hero gains 4 coins instead.

min.description:
Swap with a ::token_smoke_bomb:: Smoke bomb in range;
if you do, block the attack. You may place
the Smoke bomb into a space in range.

sabina.description:
If there are two or more friendly minions in
radius, you may retrieve a discarded card;
if you do, you may move 1 space.

If there are two or more friendly minions in
radius, you may retrieve a discarded card;
if you do, you may up to 2 spaces.

tigerclaw.description:
Move up to 2 spaces.  Take 1 or 2 coins
from an enemy hero adjacent to you;
if you do, you may move up to 2 spaces.

xargatha.description:
Before or after movement, you may move
an enemy minion in radius up to 2 spaces;
ignore heavy minion immunity.
